I"><h1 class="no_toc" id="component-settings">Component settings</h1>

<p>Each component has its settings. They can be specific for a particular component or general. In the second case, you can only change the element ID and its text.</p>

<p>These settings do not require knowledge of HTML or CSS and are of three types:</p>

<ul>
  <li>select;</li>
  <li>input;</li>
  <li>range select.</li>
</ul>

